    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "CAMPUS IS ALSO MASSIVE WHICH HAVE GYM PLAYING AREA ETC",
          "name": "Jadhav Ronit Vijay",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "STAFF HELPS U IN PROJECT AND BETTER UNDERSTANDING AND VISUALIZATION OF CONCEPTS",
          "name": "Jadhav Ronit Vijay",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Most liked thing about this college is the connectivity it has. almost located in the center of the city hence we don't has to face many problem regarding the traveling",
          "name": "Aditya Porje",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Fee structure of this college is friendly for the middle class as well.",
          "name": "Aditya Porje",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "College also provides scholarships to students.",
          "name": "Rupesh Arun Desai",
          "course_tag_name": "MCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Also college takes mock interview and for that they have separate training and placement department",
          "name": "Rupesh Arun Desai",
          "course_tag_name": "MCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teaching facilities by teachers and their personal attention ension",
          "name": "Shripad Bhutada",
          "course_tag_name": "Polytechnic"
        },
        {
          "text": "Good quality of library and classrooms .",
          "name": "Shripad Bhutada",
          "course_tag_name": "Polytechnic"
        },
        {
          "text": "Playground and other facilities provided by college",
          "name": "Shripad Bhutada",
          "course_tag_name": "Polytechnic"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college teaching staff is very supportive in each and every thig.",
          "name": "Aditya Porje",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "NO THING TO DISLIKED   THE STAFF IS VERY HELPFUL YOU GET    PLACEMENT OFFICER",
          "name": "Jadhav Ronit Vijay",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "THE STAFF IS VERY HELPFUL TO MANY THINGS TO WRITE SO NOT WRITING BUT",
          "name": "Jadhav Ronit Vijay",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "THE STAFF IS HELPFULL HELPS U IN PROJECT DOUBT SOLVING",
          "name": "Jadhav Ronit Vijay",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "As a completed 1st year in kk wagh i cam to know that there is no scholorship for any cast expect SC,NT",
          "name": "Aditya Porje",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The non-Teaching staff are not supportive hance face lot of problem with them also college does not have a proper college campus.",
          "name": "Aditya Porje",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is less availibility of the space. No of people get entry in the college with out any reason , people who does not belong to college get the entry in the campus",
          "name": "Aditya Porje",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Improve their canteen and parking area students face issues sometimes only",
          "name": "Rupesh Arun Desai",
          "course_tag_name": "MCA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Toilets were not clean regularly by the workers",
          "name": "Shripad Bhutada",
          "course_tag_name": "Polytechnic"
        },
        {
          "text": "Cleaning in the campus was not up to date",
          "name": "Shripad Bhutada",
          "course_tag_name": "Polytechnic"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some faculties were strict and not helpful",
          "name": "Shripad Bhutada",
          "course_tag_name": "Polytechnic"
        }
      ]
    },
